<div class="container hex-main-container">
  <div class='row'>
    <div class="solution-intro col-md-6 col-lg-6">
      <h2>
        <%= image_tag 'protocol_icon@2x.png', alt:'Protocols' %>
        <div>
          <span><%=t 'protocols.minititle' %></span>
          <%=t 'protocols.title' %>
        </div>
      </h2>
      <h3><%=t 'protocols.subtitle' %></h3>
      <p><%=t 'protocols.paragraph_html' %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="hex-full col-md-6 col-lg-6">
      <div class='hex-full-container'>
        <div class="circle-ripple circle-ripple-top"></div>
        <div class="circle-ripple circle-ripple-left"></div>
        <div class="circle-ripple circle-ripple-right"></div>
        <%= image_tag "hex_color_desktop@2x.png" %>
        <div class="hex-title">Smart<span>Trust</span></div>
        <div class="hex-title">Smart<span>Escrow</span></div>
        <div class="hex-title">Smart<span>Resolve</span></div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class='d-md-none'>
  <div class="center slider">
    <% %w(smartescrow smarttrust smartresolve).each do |protocol| %>
      <div class='one-slider'>
        <div class='slider-inner'>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="hex col-lg-5">
              <div class="hex-title"><%=t "protocols.#{protocol}.title_html" %></div>
              <div class='slider-image'>
                <div class="circle-ripple circle-ripple-<%=t "protocols.#{protocol}.ripple_position" %>"="protocols.#{protocol}.ripple_position" %="%"></div>
                <%= image_tag "hex_single_#{protocol}@2x.png" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class='description col-lg-7'>
              <h4>Smart<span>Escrow</span></h4>
              <p><%=t "protocols.#{protocol}.description_html" %></p>
              <!-- <ul class="features"> <% (1..4).each do |feature| %> <li> <%= image_tag "poc_checkmark.svg" %><%=t "protocols.#{protocol}.feature_#{feature}" %> </li> <% end %> </ul> -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container protocol-tabs-container">
  <div class="d-none d-md-flex">
    <div id="horizontalTab">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="#tab-1"><%= image_tag 'tab_hex_icon_1@2x.png', alt:'Protocols' %>
            <div class="tab-title">Smart Trust<span class="subtitle">Trust Protocol</span></div>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#tab-2"><%= image_tag 'tab_hex_icon_2@2x.png', alt:'Protocols' %>
            <div class="tab-title">Smart Escrow<span>Escrow System</span></div>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#tab-3"><%= image_tag 'tab_hex_icon_3@2x.png', alt:'Protocols' %>
            <div class="tab-title">Smart Resolve<span>Conflict Resolution</span></div>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div id="tab-1">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="panel-copy col-lg-12 col-xl-5">
            <div class="title">
              <span>Smart</span>
              Trust</div>
            <p>SmartTrust is a reputation algorithm that quantifies the reputation of the users with an unalterable score. This protocol gives buyers confidence to make purchases from community-trusted sellers. Provides eligibility for rewards and community
              roles for users to govern against fraud and foul play.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="protocol-benefits col-lg-12 col-xl-7">
            <div class='row'>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-5'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Reputation Scoring</div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Legitimizes Ratings & Reviews</div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-5'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>User Transparency</div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Ensures No Malicious Actors</div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="tab-2">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="panel-copy col-lg-12 col-xl-5">
            <div class="title">
              <span>Smart</span>
              Escrow</div>
            <p>SmartEscrow provides security for the buyer, seller, and node on several key phases of any purchase transaction. When locked in escrow facilitated by smart contracts, the funds are out of control from all parties ensuring payment is verified and
              fulfillment takes place.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="protocol-benefits col-lg-12 col-xl-7">
            <div class='row'>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-5'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Secure Transactions
              </div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Efficient Payment Verification
              </div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-5'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>No Intermediaries
              </div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Fulfillment Guarantee
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="tab-3">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="panel-copy col-lg-12 col-xl-5">
            <div class="title">
              <span>Smart</span>
              Resolve</div>
            <p>SmartResolve is an arbitration method that resolves disputes uniquely on a case-by-case basis facilitated by a multi-round moderation process to ensure thoroughness. Active members of the community are selected as Mediators and rewarded for their
              participation with GOOD Tokens.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="protocol-benefits col-lg-12 col-xl-7">
            <div class='row'>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-5'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Scam Prevention</div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Unbiased & Impartial System</div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-5'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Mediator Incentives</div>
              <div class='col-sm-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7'><%= image_tag "icon_poc_checkmark.svg" %>Peer-To-Peer Governance</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
